

Programs for the even-odd preconditioned Wilson-Dirac operator


check1        Gauge covariance of Qhat

check1n       Gauge covariance of Qnohat

check2        Action of Qhat on plane waves

check2n       Action of Qnohat on plane waves

check3        Hermiticity of Qhat

check3n       Hermiticity of Qnohat

check4        Gauge covariance of Qhat_dble

check4n       Gauge covariance of Qnohat_dble

check5        Action of Qhat_dble on plane waves

check5n       Action of Qnohat_dble on plane waves

check6        Hermiticity of Qhat_dble

check6n       Hermiticity of Qnohat_dble

check7        Consistency of Qeo, Qoe, Qnohat and Qhat

check8        Consistency of Qeo_dble, Qoe_dble, Qnohat_dble and Qhat_dble

